    <p >NewDeaths: <span id="covid-new-deaths"></span></p>
    <p >TotalDeaths: <span id="covid-total-deaths"></span></p>
    <p >NewRecovered: <span id="covid-new-recovered"></span></p>
    <p >TotalRecovered: <span id="covid-total-recovered"></span></p>


  </div>


</div>
